## ğŸ“Œ Overview  
The **Tableau Stock Performance Dashboard** is a powerful data visualization tool designed to provide **real-time, data-driven insights** into stock market performance.  

This project integrates **Google Sheets with Tableau** to update stock data **every hour**, ensuring up-to-date market analysis and helping investors make informed decisions.  

